data.description: Over 2000 Square Feet in this lovely open end unit townhome - where Luxury meets Location!  From the moment you walk in this sun-filled unit feels like a place you can call home.  With that in mind, your new home has an open kitchen, with a large center island perfect for preparing meals and entertaining. Rich chocolate brown hardwood floors, stainless steel appliances, beautiful counter tops, white cabinetry and subway tile offer you a clean, and crisp palette to add your touch.  Large bedrooms, with great closet space and plenty of storage throughout. There is even a luggage closet in the owner's suite. Oh how nice!  Wait, there's more! Spacious recreation room perfect for movie nights and family gatherings. Along with your one-car garage to offer you personal space and additional storage as needed.  Close to 100, 95, 295 and Arundel Mills Mall.  Move right in after settlement!!
